---
/**
 * MRT3 Project Equipment Financing: Ready Your Excavator Fleet - English
 * URL: /en/blog/mrt3-excavator-fleet-financing
 * Target: Contractor Ahmad (Excavator) - English secondary language
 * Keywords: MRT3, excavator fleet, Klang Valley infrastructure, project financing
 * Cultural Focus: Professional, opportunity-focused, ROI-driven B2B messaging
